t field name and percentage). Use multiple lines on the 250×122 screen. Adjust layout for up to 5 values.\",\"actionType\":\"code\",\"dependencies\":[\"5\"],\"priority\":0},{\"id\":\"7\",\"description\":\"Update main.cpp to wire everything together: define array of ADC pins (GPIO1..6 etc.), initialize Sensor with array, pass to Calibration, WebServer, Display. Call periodic reading and display update.\",\"actionType\":\"code\",\"dependencies\":[\"6\"],\"priority\":0},{\"id\":\"8\",\"description\":\"Verify compilation is clean, fix any issues\",\"actionType\":\"shell\",\"dependencies\":[\"7\"],\"priority\":0}]}"
