        "type": "reasoning",
        "content": "We need to patch WebServer.cpp to sync calibration to sensor after each calibration action. The code currently has:\n- POST /api/calibrate/dry: setDryValue(raw); then send\n- POST /api/calibrate/wet: setWetValue(raw); then send\n- POST /api/calibrate/reset: resetToDefaults(); then send\n\nWe need to add after each: `m_sensor->setCalibration(m_calibration->getDryValue(), m_calibration->getWetValue());`\n\nWe can try exact patch with context. Let's do three patches:\n\n1. For dry route: replace the block from line 99 to 103 with updated code.\n2. For wet route: similar.\n3. For reset route: similar.\n\nAlternative: just rewrite the whole file with the added lines. That's simpler and avoids patch complexity.\n\nWe'll use write-file to rewrite the entire WebServer.cpp with the additions.",
