        "params": {
          "task": "Rewrite platformio.ini with explicit library versions that are compatible:\n- Use me-no-dev/ESPAsyncWebServer @ 3.6.0 (the original, compatible with ESP32-S3)\n- Use me-no-dev/AsyncTCP @ 1.1.1 (required by that version)\n- Keep GxEPD2 and ArduinoJson\n\nAlso add build_flags to fix USB CDC on S3 and prevent runtime issues.\n\nCurrent content is:\n```\n[env:esp32-s3-devkitc-1]\nplatform = espressif32\nboard = esp32-s3-devkitc-1\nframework = arduino\nmonitor_speed = 115200\nlib_deps = \n    GxEPD2\n    ESPAsyncWebServer\n    AsyncTCP\n    ArduinoJson\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```\n[env:esp32-s3-devkitc-1]\nplatform = espressif32\nboard = esp32-s3-devkitc-1\nframework = arduino\nmonitor_speed = 115200\nboard_build.flash_mode = qio\nlib_deps = \n    GxEPD2\n    me-no-dev/ESPAsyncWebServer @ 3.6.0\n    me-no-dev/AsyncTCP @ 1.1.1\n    ArduinoJson\nbuild_flags = \n    -DARDUINO_USB_CDC_ON_BOOT=1\n```\n\nRead the file first, then overwrite.",
