        "command": "compress",
        "content": "## Conversation Summary\n**Turns summarized:** 12  |  **Compactions so far:** 1\n\n### User Goal\nCheck compilation of ESP32-S3 PlatformIO project and fix errors.\n\n### What Was Done\n- Created and executed a plan to compile.\n- Fixed missing GxEPD2_213_BN.h include by removing direct #include from `lib/Display/Display.h` (file was already included via GxEPD2_BW.h).\n- Fixed missing `Calibration::reset()` method by changing call to `resetToDefaults()` in `src/main.cpp`.\n- Proposed pinning library versions in `platformio.ini` to resolve dependency conflicts (ESPAsyncWebServer @ 3.6.0, AsyncTCP @ 1.1.1).\n\n### Current State\nCompilation attempts after fixes produced truncated output; full build status unknown. Last action was proposing to rewrite platformio.ini.\n\n### Pending / Next Steps\n- Rewrite platformio.ini with explicit library versions and rebuild.\n- Verify successful compilation.\n- Proceed with further features (autowatering, Web UI, hardware debug).\n\n### Key Context\n- Project path: `/home/annenskei/Документы/GitHub/polivator`\n- Board: `esp32-s3-devkitc-1`\n- PlatformIO environment: `esp32-s3-devkitc-1`\n- Library version conflict between ESPAsyncWebServer and AsyncTCP variants.",
