        "label": "Read all source files in the project to underst...",
        "content": "Summary: The project is an ESP32-S3 based plant watering system with moisture sensors, calibration storage in NVS, a web server for configuration and status, and an e-ink display. Key classes: Calibration (manages sensor config via Preferences), SensorManager (reads analog sensors, converts to percentage), WebServer (REST API, web UI, WiFi management), Display (e-ink display using GxEPD2). The main.cpp ties them together but has inconsistencies: expects a Sensor object instead of SensorManager, uses wrong method names (readRaw vs getRaw). Also Types.h missing, assumed to define MAX_SENSORS and SensorConfig. Overall structure is modular but needs cleanup.",
