ough the web interface (not just at first boot). They may want a configuration page.\n\nLet's start by reading relevant source files to understand the current implementation. We'll read Display.cpp, main.cpp, and maybe WebServer/index.h to see the web interface content.\n\nBut first, let's recall what we have in memory about the display.",
