        "content": "User working on ESP32 polivator project, previously added WiFi content-type fix and sensor delete feature. Now integrating e-paper display from WeActStudio. Examined GitHub repo and example for ESP32S3. Identified need to fix Display.cpp: correct init parameters (borrowed from example: display.init(115200)), use firstPage/nextPage update method, remove redundant fillScreen before display. Build succeeded earlier.",
