DevKitC-1-N8.\n- PlatformIO project at `/home/annenskei/Документы/GitHub/polivator`.\n- SPI pins: SCLK=18, MOSI=21 (not changed).\n- Web server likely manages sensor list (add/remove).\n- Partial update requires checking `hasFastPartialUpdate` and using `nextPage()`.",
