        "content": "We need to redesign the web UI (index.h) with IBM Plex font, add a pinout page. Also we need to download the font from Google Fonts and embed via @import.\n\nCurrent index.h already uses IBM Plex Sans via Google Fonts link. The design is already somewhat Carbon-like with CSS variables and light/dark themes. But user wants to add a separate pinout menu/page.\n\nWe'll add a navigation bar with tabs: Dashboard, Pinout, Settings. The pinout page will display the GPIO assignments for display and sensors. We'll keep theme toggle and OTA button.\n\nSince index.h is huge (701 lines), we should rewrite it completely with the following:\n\n- Modern IBM Plex design (already done)\n- Nav bar with tabs: Dashboard (sensors), Pinout, Settings\n- Pinout page: table with component -> pin mapping\n- Settings page: existing WiFi settings + update interval + priority\n\nWe need to make sure all existing functionality works: SSE, calibration, name editing, delete/enable, OTA, theme toggle.\n\nWe'll write the whole index.h file as a PROGMEM raw string.\n\nLet's plan the structure:\n\n- CSS: IBM Plex Sans, Carbon-like tokens, responsive\n- HTML: nav bar, three pages (dashboard, pinout, settings), modals\n- JS: SSE, calibration functions, tab switching, settings load/save, OTA, theme\n\nWe'll generate the file.",
