        "type": "reasoning",
        "content": "The user wants me to rewrite the web UI (lib/WebServer/index.h) to include IBM Plex font, a navigation bar with tabs (Dashboard, Pinout, Settings), a Pinout tab showing a table with pin assignments, preserving all existing functionality (SSE, calibration, name edit, delete/enable, OTA update, theme toggle). I need to write the complete file.\n\nLet me create the new index.h with:\n1. IBM Plex Sans font (already imported)\n2. Navigation tabs: Dashboard, Pinout, Settings\n3. Dashboard: existing sensor cards with gauges, name inputs, buttons\n4. Pinout: table showing display pins (BUSY, RES, DC, CS, SCK, MOSI) and sensor pins (0-4)\n5. Settings: WiFi SSID/password, interval, priority, theme toggle, OTA update\n6. All existing JavaScript for SSE, calibration, name edit, delete/enable\n7. Theme toggle preserving state in localStorage\n\nI need to be thorough and include all the JavaScript logic. This will be a large file.",
