        "type": "reasoning",
        "content": "The swarm has completed successfully. I now have consolidated report from synthesizer. I need to present the results to the user.\n\nThe user asked \"в режиме swarm проанализируй что можно было бы улучшить\" which means \"in swarm mode, analyze what could be improved\". The swarm has done that and produced a final report.\n\nI should output the final consolidated report from the synthesizer as the answer, possibly with a brief message summarizing the findings.",
        "timestamp": 1781620266297
